text: Violeta Lastakauskaitė (born 28 December 1965) is a Lithuanian rower. She competed in the women's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:Lithuanian female rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Lithuania Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics
